Capital recovery factor (CRF): this critical parameter is relevant in calculating the value or cost of an annuity. It is represented by the below formula that was reported by Adaramola et al. [31].

15LCOE=I+∑t=1nAt1+in∑t=1nMel1+in\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
