				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$ \mathrm{LCOE}=\frac{I+{\sum}_{t=1}^n\frac{A_t\ }{{\left(1+i\right)}^n}}{\sum_{t=1}^n\frac{Mel}{{\left(1+i\right)}^n}}\kern12.25em $$\end{document}where I = capital costs/investment costs ($), At = annual total costs/operation and maintenance costs, and Mel = annual energy/electricity generated (kWh).
